00:13:48.688 --> 00:13:52.288
Namun Krishna baru
saja memasuki hidupku.

00:13:52.768 --> 00:13:54.248
Aku takut memikirkan
bagaimana jika

00:13:54.328 --> 00:13:57.288
seseorang mengambil
Krishna dariku.

00:13:57.328 --> 00:13:58.688
Saaransh bersama kalian berdua selama ..

